page.title: 11FOOD
page.content: This is the food eaten by an 11 year old in 1985 MONDAY Frosties with milk,one egg sandwich,a packet of crisps,12 mini cookies,coke, apple,chicken,baked potatoe,peas and gravy. TUESDAY Frosties with milk,one egg sandwich,a packet of crisps,drifter,an orange, coke,two shepherds pies and some trifle. WEDNESDAY Frosties with milk,one cheese sandwich orangeade,crisps,chocolate crispy, sweet and sour pork and some chocolate. THURSDAY Frosties,egg sandwiches,coke,crisps, chocolate crispy and spagetti bolenase.
